727441f-a.title: Queens: Mount Olivet Crescent - 60th Avenue
727441f-a.text:
Mount Olivet Crescent, east side, between Sixtieth Ave., and 60th Road showing Chris Aukerbauer's(7) farmhouse. C. Anglebach, who owned
this property in 1873, sold it to Enst Nurge (09244.
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
